Part 2
(a)  a private retirement scheme approved by the Commission under the Capital
Markets and Services Act 2007;
(b)  a unit trust scheme approved, authorized or recognized by the Commission
under the Capital Markets and Services Act 2007;
(c)  any other capital market funds as may be specified by the Commission.
